{"actor":"eykd","comment":null,"created_at":"2026-03-20T19:54:00Z","event_type":"status_changed","id":"397cab66-cf28-4764-96db-44d4b482b060","issue_id":"clawtask-jef.3","new_value":"{\"status\":\"in_progress\"}","old_value":"{\"id\":\"clawtask-jef.3\",\"title\":\"BUG: API sign-out (POST /api/auth/sign-out) returns 500 and fails to invalidate session\",\"description\":\"POST /api/auth/sign-out returns HTTP 500 with an empty body. The session remains valid after the call. The form-based sign-out works correctly. Root cause: the route in worker.ts passes the request to better-auth, which returns a 500 response (not an exception). The try/catch only handles thrown exceptions.\",\"status\":\"open\",\"priority\":0,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"david@worldsenoughstudios.com\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-20T19:45:51Z\",\"created_by\":\"eykd\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-20T19:45:51Z\"}"}
{"actor":"eykd","comment":null,"created_at":"2026-03-20T19:54:12Z","event_type":"status_changed","id":"df88aaaa-7c8f-4459-91e2-949be0f82ce9","issue_id":"clawtask-jef.3","new_value":"{\"status\":\"in_progress\"}","old_value":"{\"id\":\"clawtask-jef.3\",\"title\":\"BUG: API sign-out (POST /api/auth/sign-out) returns 500 and fails to invalidate session\",\"description\":\"POST /api/auth/sign-out returns HTTP 500 with an empty body. The session remains valid after the call. The form-based sign-out works correctly. Root cause: the route in worker.ts passes the request to better-auth, which returns a 500 response (not an exception). The try/catch only handles thrown exceptions.\",\"status\":\"in_progress\",\"priority\":0,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"david@worldsenoughstudios.com\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-20T19:45:51Z\",\"created_by\":\"eykd\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-20T19:54:01Z\"}"}
