{"actor":"eykd","comment":null,"created_at":"2026-03-20T20:05:51Z","event_type":"status_changed","id":"3f073277-217e-4828-80e2-7a562e53fc0d","issue_id":"clawtask-jef.2","new_value":"{\"status\":\"in_progress\"}","old_value":"{\"id\":\"clawtask-jef.2\",\"title\":\"BUG: auth-store.js hardcodes __Host-auth_status cookie name -- auth always false on localhost\",\"description\":\"The server correctly drops the __Host- prefix on non-HTTPS localhost (setting cookie as auth_status=1), but auth-store.js checks for __Host-auth_status=1. Result: isAuthenticated is always false on localhost. Navbar always shows Sign In, dashboardGuard always redirects away from /dashboard/.\",\"status\":\"open\",\"priority\":0,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"david@worldsenoughstudios.com\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-20T19:45:49Z\",\"created_by\":\"eykd\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-20T19:45:49Z\"}"}
