{"actor":"eykd","comment":null,"created_at":"2026-03-20T21:06:31Z","event_type":"status_changed","id":"34e9fdbf-ad27-4961-83fd-b20e7069e256","issue_id":"clawtask-jef.13","new_value":"{\"status\":\"in_progress\"}","old_value":"{\"id\":\"clawtask-jef.13\",\"title\":\"BUG: handleGetSignIn ignores redirectTo for already-authenticated users\",\"description\":\"When an already-authenticated user hits /auth/sign-in?redirectTo=/dashboard/, they are redirected to / unconditionally, discarding the redirectTo parameter. Compounds with the localhost auth cookie bug.\",\"status\":\"open\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"david@worldsenoughstudios.com\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-20T19:46:22Z\",\"created_by\":\"eykd\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-20T19:46:22Z\"}"}
{"actor":"eykd","comment":null,"created_at":"2026-03-20T21:10:24Z","event_type":"closed","id":"76ee6c7c-2346-4491-8118-aa4f43ea22d1","issue_id":"clawtask-jef.13","new_value":"Closed","old_value":""}
{"actor":"eykd","comment":null,"created_at":"2026-03-20T21:13:39Z","event_type":"status_changed","id":"efa4fea8-4951-4ce1-a7a5-767bdfcc904a","issue_id":"clawtask-jef.12","new_value":"{\"status\":\"in_progress\"}","old_value":"{\"id\":\"clawtask-jef.12\",\"title\":\"BUG: Huge Content-Length header causes server to hang (potential DoS)\",\"description\":\"Sending Content-Length: 999999999 with a small body causes the connection to time out. No request body size limit is enforced at the HTTP layer for API routes. Form-based auth handlers have MAX_BODY_BYTES=4096 but API routes do not.\",\"status\":\"open\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"david@worldsenoughstudios.com\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-20T19:46:14Z\",\"created_by\":\"eykd\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-20T19:46:14Z\"}"}
{"actor":"eykd","comment":null,"created_at":"2026-03-20T21:20:36Z","event_type":"closed","id":"61aa0edc-b98d-4952-8cf1-0e32f7890d49","issue_id":"clawtask-jef.12","new_value":"Closed","old_value":""}
{"actor":"eykd","comment":null,"created_at":"2026-03-20T21:23:46Z","event_type":"status_changed","id":"2e5cb8d5-d59f-4b40-b9bb-4ed775e1447f","issue_id":"clawtask-jef.11","new_value":"{\"status\":\"in_progress\"}","old_value":"{\"id\":\"clawtask-jef.11\",\"title\":\"BUG: Unsupported HTTP methods return 404 instead of 405 on /api/v1/*\",\"description\":\"PUT, DELETE, PATCH on /api/v1/inbox return 404 with 'Not found'. Per RFC 7231, should return 405 with an Allow header. Auth routes correctly return 405 but API routes do not.\",\"status\":\"open\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"david@worldsenoughstudios.com\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-20T19:46:12Z\",\"created_by\":\"eykd\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-20T19:46:12Z\"}"}
