{"actor":"eykd","comment":null,"created_at":"2026-03-21T05:21:22Z","event_type":"status_changed","id":"774e44b3-8ed5-46a9-a8b0-d7a85c66394e","issue_id":"clawtask-rwt.1.18","new_value":"{\"status\":\"in_progress\"}","old_value":"{\"id\":\"clawtask-rwt.1.18\",\"title\":\"bug: sign-up page has no terms of service or privacy policy links\",\"description\":\"The sign-up form does not reference Terms of Service or Privacy Policy. Users creating accounts should see and/or agree to terms. The footer links exist on Hugo pages but the auth pages (rendered by Worker) have no footer. For legal compliance, users should be informed of terms when creating an account.\",\"status\":\"open\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"david@worldsenoughstudios.com\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-21T05:14:09Z\",\"created_by\":\"eykd\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-21T05:14:09Z\"}"}
