{"actor":"eykd","comment":null,"created_at":"2026-03-21T05:25:20Z","event_type":"status_changed","id":"a351d2e9-64f6-4036-8695-493c9f70a7a8","issue_id":"clawtask-rwt.1.17","new_value":"{\"status\":\"in_progress\"}","old_value":"{\"id\":\"clawtask-rwt.1.17\",\"title\":\"bug: reset-password page missing confirm password field and requirements hint\",\"description\":\"The reset-password form has only one password field with no confirm field (sign-up form has one). Also missing the 'Must be at least 12 characters' hint text that sign-up shows, though it does have minlength=12. Users could mistype new password with no way to catch it. Inconsistent UX between sign-up and reset-password.\",\"status\":\"open\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"david@worldsenoughstudios.com\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-21T05:14:08Z\",\"created_by\":\"eykd\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-21T05:14:08Z\"}"}
